Package: rpart.translator
Type: Package
Title: Tool For Simplifying Decision Trees into Table Readable Format
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Jason Wittenauer <jwittenauer@huronconsultinggroup.com> [aut, cre]", 
    "Justin Silva <jsilva@huronconsultinggroup> [aut]"
  ))
Description: This package contains a tool for formating a rpart decision tree model into a table of rules and subrules. This table is in a database friendly format to provide transparency into the model decision making process.
